        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The MOVING reference member state of this VC (Value Chain) is ITALY UNIMOL and UNIPI. The reference MOVING Card ID of this VC is VC 50 IT. The farm has 35 cows in production, of the Grigio Alpina breed and the Original Brouw breed; the main products are &amp;apos;Formai de Ceresegn &amp;apos;cheese, aged from one to three years, Formagella, with variable seasoning from 20-90 days, and butter.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


