        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is unspecified. The innovation start to spread also in this very traditional value chain. The innovation is related to the whole VC. The land use systems involved are Grassland and Natural land. The local assets include Natural.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N112_VC_50_IT/event/ev2 -->


    <NamedIndividual rdf:about="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N112_VC_50_IT/event/ev2">
